snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, Will Other Star's Confessions CHANGE Anything?
snippet.description:
As always, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have been on everyone's lips since their divorce. No matter what, someone somewhere is talking about them, including us. We've heard many things about both of them the past 4 years, especially during the defamation court case, but what do the people that know them best have to say? Did Depp's Pirates of the Caribbean co-stars come to his aid?  Did Johnny's ex's, Winona Ryder and Vanessa Paradis, share any insight into their past relationships with the actor? And who is on Heard's side? #JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #OrlandoBloom 

👉You might be interested in this video: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard: Will The Judge Finally Uncover The Truth? https://youtu.be/Qw22Plchrc8
